{"id":55355,"type":6,"name":"2ndハウス","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/5b/95/55355_jgA34.jpg","summary":"サラリーマンの三澤耕一は、妻と子供に見放され、自分の居場所をなくしていた。そんなある日、会社の同僚3人と自由奔放の部屋・セカンドハウスを借りることを画策した。\r\n一方、女優を目指して上京した中嶋亜希は居心地の悪かった先輩の家から独立し、不動産屋へ足を運ぶ。しかし、亜希が目を付けていた物件は、既に三澤たちのものになっていたのだ。\r\n数日後、飲み屋で偶然鉢合わせした三澤と亜希。物件を巡って交渉した末、三澤が折れる形で亜希に譲渡した。そんなこんなで2人の奇妙な新生活がここから始まったのである。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>第二个家</li><li><span>放送星期: </span>金曜日</li><li><span>别名: </span>2nd House</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>second House</li><li><span>集数: </span>12</li><li><span>开始: </span>2006年1月13日</li><li><span>结束: </span>2006年3月31日</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>日本</li><li><span>语言: </span>日语</li>","collection":{"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"2006","count":1},{"name":"日剧","count":1}],"eps":[{"id":214569,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214569","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214570,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214570","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214571,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214571","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214572,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214572","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214573,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214573","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214574,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214574","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214575,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214575","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":214576,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/214576","type":0,"sort":8,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":21